== Sant Antonik Noven ==
'''Saint Anthony Novena'''

[[File:Guercino Antonio Bambino.jpg|thumb|Saint Anthony of Padua with the Infant Christ by Guercino, 1656, Bologna, Italy]]


Onodvant Sant Antoni, visvaxea ani bhettlelea chakra Jezuchea ani Mariechea, ani zolltea divea Sant Francisk Asizachea poile Ordichea, tuka bhorla Devan denneamnim ani soimbhavorte podven soglleam bhutancher and devcharancher, je raj korta hea sonvsarant, ghalun tankam soglleank tuje khoxe khal, ani korun tuka ek upkar vanttpi, khalteponnim tuka ami ulo marum zalear, rokddench pollta mornn, chuki, khorgam, devchar  ani piddecho voso, piddevontank mellta bholaiki, addkhollink sampoddleleank adhar, thonttimpangllim borim zatat, doriachem modd thanddauta, na zatat soglle sonkoxtt, duspott'tat soglle dusman, ugtte ani lipun asat te, nivartat ujeachea ani dhornkampichea sokoxttantle, ani sanddleleo vostu melltat, xekhim soglle upkar melltat tuje ochorianche podvochea bollan, ami magtanv tuje lagim, vinot korun Jezu lagim, zo lhan burgeachea rupan tuje vengent ietalo gheunk apurbaieche humane, ani tache bhov bhagevonti Maie lagim jicho tum vortoloi ek visvaxi chakor, melloun ghe amkam kuddichea ani atmeach upkar zanchi amkam choddh goroz, odhik korun....

''(hanga mag tuzo upkar )''

amkam pav soglleam addkhollimnim, khonti-dukhinim ami tankunk sorginchi vatt ani pavuncheak sasnnachea sukhak.  

'''''Amen'''''

''(Amchea Bapa, Noman Marie ani Mhoima Bapak )''

